JUNO.
Oh, will you really put me on that?
Say you will.
MRS. LUNN.
Well, perhaps I will.
[He kisses her hand].
Now don't begin abusing the privilege.
JUNO.
May I call you by your Christian name?
MRS. LUNN.
No: it's too long.
You can't go about calling a woman Seraphita.
JUNO [ecstatically] Seraphita!
MRS. LUNN.
